    <article>
        <p>I use the javascript console as a calculator, and it is funny when binary &lt;- -&gt; decimal rounding/conversion errors pop up unexpectedly.  </p>
<p>This is a good reason to be careful when doing if(x==someNumber) conditionals in your code.</p>

